{"tid":774673,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"YouTube 發表報告稱 Galaxy Note 9 睇片最正　iPhone 榜上無名","createTime":"2018-08-10T13:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T10:31:51.000Z","uid":85180,"like":26,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d62cd6924990c1cd5d188100503178b567c7cb16","tid":774673,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T13:32:48.000Z","msg":"YouTube 發表報告稱 Galaxy Note 9 睇片最正　iPhone 榜上無名<br />\n<br />\nYouTube 剛發佈了 《YouTube Device Report》，推薦收看影片的最佳設備，並稱它為「Signature device」。而名單的榜首是 Samsung 在昨天發佈的 Galaxy Note 9，iPhone 手機則榜上無名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/00-694x370.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F00-694x370.png&h=1c4cfa90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n名單上的設備支援觀看 360 度影片﹑備有高動態範圍﹑高幀率﹑4K 解碼等特色，還有新一代編解碼器和可靠的 DRM 性能。<br />\n<br />\n報告推薦了 18 款設備，除了 Samsung Galaxy Note 9 外，還有其他十分受歡迎的手機，例如Pixel 2 XL﹑ OnePlus 6 和 HTC U12 Plus，但榜上沒有一部是 iPhone 手機。另外，Apple 不支援由 Google 開發的 VP9 視頻編解碼器，這就是為什麼 Safari 用戶無法以 4K 觀看視頻的原因。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2018-08-10-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884.40.13-566x580.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2018-08-10-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25884.40.13-566x580.png&h=1c7fe5f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"418f3bf17ed11fd2af1dc31807bffa001ebbb225","tid":774673,"uid":77569,"like":20,"dislike":36,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T13:35:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33a93b09faaf1ad48757b948f06ec5a955b7eab5","tid":774673,"uid":164092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T13:36:12.000Z","msg":"部部都有嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3